Say '''Apayao''' et kumatlo ya klase luyag na [[Cordillera Administrative Region]], [[Pilipinas]]. Unong ed 2010 Census, say papulasyon to et 112,636 totoo. <br>
Walay kabaleg tan sukat to ya  4,413.35 kilometro kuwadrado. Say dialling code to et 74. Say kapital to et Kabugao.  
        
